{
  "name": "memoweft",
  "version": "0.3.0",
  "description": "换个模型，AI 就把用户忘光了。MemoWeft 给 AI 助手一块带得走的长期记忆——而且不把猜的当真的。Long-term memory for AI assistants: portable across models, and it keeps facts and guesses apart.",
  "keywords": ["llm", "agent", "memory", "cognition", "user-profile"],
  "license": "MIT",
  "engines": { "node": ">=20" },
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "git+https://github.com/memoweft/memoweft.git"
  },
  "bugs": {
    "url": "https://github.com/memoweft/memoweft/issues"
  },
  "homepage": "https://github.com/memoweft/memoweft#readme",
  "type": "module",
  "main": "dist/index.js",
  "types": "dist/index.d.ts",
  "exports": {
    ".": {
      "types": "./dist/index.d.ts",
      "default": "./dist/index.js"
    }
  },
  "files": ["dist/**/*.js", "dist/**/*.d.ts", "README.md", "README.zh-CN.md", "CHANGELOG.md", "LICENSE"],
  "workspaces": [".", "apps/*", "plugins/*"],
  "scripts": {
    "typecheck": "tsc -p tsconfig.json",
    "test": "node --test \"tests/**/*.test.ts\"",
    "test:coverage": "node --test --experimental-test-coverage \"tests/**/*.test.ts\"",
    "test:e2e": "node --test \"tests/**/*.e2e.ts\"",
    "lint": "eslint .",
    "format": "prettier --check .",
    "testbench": "node testbench/server.mjs",
    "collector": "node plugins/collector-active-window/run.mjs",
    "experience": "node testbench/server.mjs",
    "build": "tsc -p tsconfig.build.json",
    "bench": "node bench/bulk-updateProfile.mjs",
    "smoke:dist": "node tests/smoke/dist-smoke.mjs",
    "dev:core": "tsc -p tsconfig.build.json --watch",
    "prepublishOnly": "npm run typecheck && npm test && npm run build"
  },
  "dependencies": {},
  "peerDependencies": {
    "better-sqlite3": ">=9"
  },
  "peerDependenciesMeta": {
    "better-sqlite3": { "optional": true }
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "typescript": "^5.7.0",
    "@types/node": "^24.0.0",
    "better-sqlite3": ">=9",
    "eslint": "^9.0.0",
    "@eslint/js": "^9.0.0",
    "typescript-eslint": "^8.0.0",
    "prettier": "^3.0.0"
  },
  "_comment": "依赖最小化：runtime dependencies 必须为空——'零运行时依赖'指这个。better-sqlite3 是【可选 peer 依赖】（Node 20/22 才需要，装不装用户自己定），可选 peer 不算破戒。devDependencies 里的 better-sqlite3 仅供多版本测试矩阵用（Node 24 默认走内置 node:sqlite，测零依赖路径时会 rm 掉它）。存储 / HTTP / 日志优先 Node 内置（node:sqlite、node:http、node:fs）；新增 runtime 依赖须有明确理由，默认拒绝。"
}
